			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>When you stand before this wrought-iron framed mirror, you can change your looks to reflect your every whim.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Wondrous Item</b><b>:</b> Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Standard Action)</b></p><p>You gain the appearance of a member of any humanoid race of the same size category as you. Your clothing and equipment alter appearance as you desire. The illusion doesn't alter</p><p>sound or texture, so a creature listening to you or touching you might detect the illusion. The illusion lasts until you leave the lair where the mirror resides, or until you end the effect as a free action.</p>",
